result.title: A little problem with 294 ranking
result.content:
Hi, the problem is following. I solved all the tasks at 293 and it passed 2 hours since the contest's end, all the results are published, but i still got "Running on test 49" status on C (only in my "submissions" tab). If you open the submission window you can see that it's passed 49-th and even 50 and 51-th tests but the status are not updated. Also in "Contests" tab it says that i solved 4 and am 14-th though with 4 problems i'd be like 100-th.

I would like to know if it's a bug.
